<H1>Michael and Orietta Ruggier</H1>

<P>
<IMG border="0" src="images/Michaelandorietta.jpg" align="left" width="248" height="261" hspace="15" vspace="8"><P>&nbsp;<P>&nbsp;<P>Well, guys and girls, the last time we had a 
    chance to see a large contingent of the Ruggier clan was at our wedding, and 
    that was 3½ years ago. We still have the fondest memories of that day and 
    the party the day before when Claire, Natasha and Michelle managed to 
    surprise Hilda and Norman to such good effect. We really cannot express our 
    joy at having so many of the ‘clan’ there to share such a special day with 
    us!<P>&nbsp;<P>When we first met we shared our dreams and aspirations. One of those 
    shared dreams was to travel and see the world…….. Well, since our wedding we 
    have lived in three different continents! This is actually our fourth house 
    in as many years, although surrounded as we are by memories purchased during 
    our travels it feels as much of a home as in the previous ones. It is a 
    delightful apartment in Houston complete with pool and BBQ pit (of course!) 
    and we are right in the middle of the ‘action’, which over here means lots 
    of restaurants……<TABLE border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse: collapse" bordercolor="#111111" width="100%">
