<P>As you all know by now September this year brought us our most cherished 
blessing. After three long years of struggling with infertility we finally got 
pregnant. Now let it not be said that Michael will ever do things by half….. so 
why should this be any different? It transpires we are having triplets which to 
us in a never ending source of delight and merriment!!!! </P>
<P>The babies are due on June 11th but are expected to come in early May, so we 
are packing in our last travels for a while. Orietta’s father and step mum came 
to Houston in November and we underwent a fabulous trip to Santa Fe, the canyons 
of Utah, Las Vegas, Sedona and Tucson. We saw beautiful natural phenomena (and I 
am not talking of Michael here!) and followed suit by plunging ourselves in the 
decadence of Las Vegas! </P>
